name: Supreme Home Care Agency of Ny INC

narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Supreme Home Care Agency of Ny INC is a Home Health provider based in Flushing, NY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $58.4M in Medicaid payments across 472K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $58.4M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
